<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .clip-area {
            position: relative;
            margin: 30px auto;
            width: 800px;
            height: 600px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #e3f2fd 25%, transparent 25%), 
                        linear-gradient(-45deg, #e3f2fd 25%, transparent 25%), 
                        linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 75%, #e3f2fd 75%), 
                        linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 75%, #e3f2fd 75%);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            background-position: 0 0, 0 10px, 10px -10px, -10px 0px;
            border: 2px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .clip-target {
            position: absolute;
            top: <%= clipRegion.y %>px;
            left: <%= clipRegion.x %>px;
            width: <%= clipRegion.width %>px;
            height: <%= clipRegion.height %>px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            border: 3px solid #dc3545;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .coordinates {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .corner-markers {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        .corner-marker {
            position: absolute;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 3px solid #dc3545;
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.2);
        }
        
        .corner-tl {
            top: -3px;
            left: -3px;
            border-right: none;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .corner-tr {
            top: -3px;
            right: -3px;
            border-left: none;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .corner-bl {
            bottom: -3px;
            left: -3px;
            border-right: none;
            border-top: none;
        }
        
        .corner-br {
            bottom: -3px;
            right: -3px;
            border-left: none;
            border-top: none;
        }
        
        .measurement-lines {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        .measure-line {
            position: absolute;
            background: #007bff;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
        
        .measure-horizontal {
            height: 2px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
        }
        
        .measure-vertical {
            width: 2px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .measure-label {
            position: absolute;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .info-box h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #495057;
        }
        
        .coordinate-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 15px 0;
            background: white;
        }
        
        .coordinate-table th,
        .coordinate-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        
        .coordinate-table th {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .current-coords {
            background: #e7f3ff !important;
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .testing-info {
            background: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #0c5460;
        }
        
        .cli-example {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p>This page provides a clearly marked rectangle for testing image clipping functionality. The red-bordered green area represents the target clipping region.</p>
        
        <div class="clip-area">
            <div class="clip-target">
                <div style="font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px;">üéØ CLIP TARGET</div>
                <div class="coordinates">
                    X: <%= clipRegion.x %>px, Y: <%= clipRegion.y %>px<br>
                    Width: <%= clipRegion.width %>px, Height: <%= clipRegion.height %>px
                </div>
                <div style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    This area should be captured<br>
                    when using --clip option
                </div>
                
                <div class="corner-markers">
                    <div class="corner-marker corner-tl"></div>
                    <div class="corner-marker corner-tr"></div>
                    <div class="corner-marker corner-bl"></div>
                    <div class="corner-marker corner-br"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Measurement lines -->
            <div class="measurement-lines">
                <!-- Top line -->
                <div class="measure-line measure-horizontal" style="top: <%= clipRegion.y %>px;"></div>
                <div class="measure-label" style="top: <%= clipRegion.y - 20 %>px; left: <%= clipRegion.x + clipRegion.width/2 - 30 %>px;">
                    Y: <%= clipRegion.y %>px
                </div>
                
                <!-- Left line -->
                <div class="measure-line measure-vertical" style="left: <%= clipRegion.x %>px;"></div>
                <div class="measure-label" style="left: <%= clipRegion.x - 60 %>px; top: <%= clipRegion.y + clipRegion.height/2 - 10 %>px;">
                    X: <%= clipRegion.x %>px
                </div>
                
                <!-- Right line -->
                <div class="measure-line measure-vertical" style="left: <%= clipRegion.x + clipRegion.width %>px;"></div>
                <div class="measure-label" style="left: <%= clipRegion.x + clipRegion.width + 10 %>px; top: <%= clipRegion.y + clipRegion.height/2 - 10 %>px;">
                    <%= clipRegion.x + clipRegion.width %>px
                </div>
                
                <!-- Bottom line -->
                <div class="measure-line measure-horizontal" style="top: <%= clipRegion.y + clipRegion.height %>px;"></div>
                <div class="measure-label" style="top: <%= clipRegion.y + clipRegion.height + 5 %>px; left: <%= clipRegion.x + clipRegion.width/2 - 30 %>px;">
                    <%= clipRegion.y + clipRegion.height %>px
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-box">
                <h4>üìê Current Clip Region</h4>
                <table class="coordinate-table">
                    <tr>
                        <th>Property</th>
                        <th>Value</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="current-coords">
                        <td>X (Left)</td>
                        <td><%= clipRegion.x %>px</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="current-coords">
                        <td>Y (Top)</td>
                        <td><%= clipRegion.y %>px</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="current-coords">
                        <td>Width</td>
                        <td><%= clipRegion.width %>px</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr class="current-coords">
                        <td>Height</td>
                        <td><%= clipRegion.height %>px</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Right Edge</td>
                        <td><%= clipRegion.x + clipRegion.width %>px</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Bottom Edge</td>
                        <td><%= clipRegion.y + clipRegion.height %>px</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h4>üéØ Standard Clip Regions</h4>
                <table class="coordinate-table">
                    <tr>
                        <th>Region</th>
                        <th>Coordinates</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Top-Left Quarter</td>
                        <td>0,0,400,300</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Center Square</td>
                        <td>200,150,400,300</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Current Target</td>
                        <td class="current-coords"><%= clipRegion.x %>,<%= clipRegion.y %>,<%= clipRegion.width %>,<%= clipRegion.height %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Full Width Strip</td>
                        <td>0,200,800,200</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Right Half</td>
                        <td>400,0,400,600</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h4>üñºÔ∏è Image Format Options</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>PNG:</strong> Best for screenshots with transparency</li>
                    <li><strong>JPEG:</strong> Smaller file size, good for photos</li>
                    <li><strong>WebP:</strong> Modern format, excellent compression</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h5>Quality Settings:</h5>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>100:</strong> Maximum quality (largest file)</li>
                    <li><strong>90:</strong> High quality (recommended)</li>
                    <li><strong>75:</strong> Good quality (balanced)</li>
                    <li><strong>50:</strong> Medium quality (smaller file)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="testing-info">
            <h3>üß™ Clipping Test Instructions</h3>
            
            <h4>CLI Command for Current Region:</h4>
            <div class="cli-example">
printeer convert \
  --url "http://localhost:4000/image/clip-target?x=<%= clipRegion.x %>&y=<%= clipRegion.y %>&width=<%= clipRegion.width %>&height=<%= clipRegion.height %>" \
  --clip "<%= clipRegion.x %>,<%= clipRegion.y %>,<%= clipRegion.width %>,<%= clipRegion.height %>" \
  --output clip-test.png
            </div>
            
            <h4>Alternative Clip Formats:</h4>
            <div class="cli-example">
# Object format
--clip "x:<%= clipRegion.x %>,y:<%= clipRegion.y %>,width:<%= clipRegion.width %>,height:<%= clipRegion.height %>"

# JSON format  
--clip '{"x":<%= clipRegion.x %>,"y":<%= clipRegion.y %>,"width":<%= clipRegion.width %>,"height":<%= clipRegion.height %>}'
            </div>
            
            <h4>Expected Results:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Output image should contain only the green target area</li>
                <li>Image dimensions should be <%= clipRegion.width %>√ó<%= clipRegion.height %> pixels</li>
                <li>Red corner markers should be visible at the edges</li>
                <li>Target text and coordinates should be clearly readable</li>
                <li>Background pattern should not be visible outside the clip region</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>Test Variations:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Try different clip regions by changing URL parameters</li>
                <li>Test with different image formats (PNG, JPEG, WebP)</li>
                <li>Vary quality settings for JPEG/WebP output</li>
                <li>Test edge cases (clip region at page boundaries)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background: #e9ecef; border-radius: 6px; text-align: center;">
            <h4>üéØ Clip Region Validation</h4>
            <p style="font-weight: bold; margin: 10px 0;">
                Target Region: <%= clipRegion.x %>,<%= clipRegion.y %>,<%= clipRegion.width %>,<%= clipRegion.height %>
            </p>
            <p style="color: #6c757d; font-style: italic;">
                The clipped image should contain only the green area with red borders and target text.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>